name: Wonderly Finance xETH
description: About Wonderly Finance XETH Token (XETH) The Wonderful Protocol is a DeFi project aimed at developing and popularizing synthetic tokens for multiple L1 & L2 Ecosystems. Imagine having exposure to the price of FTM, AVAX, ETH, or any other token without actually owning it. XETH is a synthetic ERC-20 token on Arbitrum One that is pegged 1:1 to the price of ETH.
